hopobject.body: Please wait shills black mask palsu Others might detect overcompensation: a state-school-educated woman from a working-class home who is encountering the intimidating public-school culture for the first time, and doesn’t want to let her children down. As Carole must have surmised, only aristocrats can get away with scruffy clothes and stale sandwiches. Those who were raised on Mother’s Pride need steady nerves, tenacity and, if possible, a mother’s pride to stay the course. If you’re not to the manor (or the manner) born, you have to try that much harder.
